data.title: War Diary; George Leach Colonel 151st Field Artillery Rainbow Division
data.meta_description: Pioneer Printers, 1923. First edition. Hardcover. 20 x 14 cm. Octavo; Gray cloth with gilt lettering to cover and spine. 205pp. Covering the September 1917 through May 1919. SIGNED, and inscribed To William Kempton Jr so you will know about the war your distinguised dad was in, George Leach . Some fading to spine and front cover. Bottom corners lightly bumped. very good. Item #65914
